name: BRYAN
desc: Bryan is known for creating natural-looking, long-lasting color; seamless long layer cuts, razor cuts, and beautiful finishing techniques.

name: CARRIE
desc: Carrie loves doing classic shapes that last, men’s cuts from classic to crazy, and razor cuts.

name: DAVID
desc: David loves to cut & style long, curly and wavy textures as well as natural ombre highlights.

name: GLEEN
desc: Glenn loves to do short womens cuts, men's barbering, long layers, and lived in, natural hilites.

name: HYLEE
desc: Haylee loves solving all her clients' hair challenges! She enjoys doing mens and women's cuts on all lengths and textures and loves adding dimension and style to every guest's hair. She also loves hair painting and blonding.

name: HEATHER
desc: Heather loves working with all hair lengths and specializes in accentuating her clients natural textures to create easy wash and go styles. *Heathers color services are booked by consultation only.

name: HOLLY
desc: Holly loves doing sun-kissed blondes, dimensional brunettes, and radiant redheads.

name: JENNA
desc: Jenna specializes in blondes of all tones like natural blended highlights, beachy lived-in color, baby lights, and sun-kissed brunettes. She loves color corrections and color matching for natural grey coverage and blending. She creates haircuts that are low maintenance and low fuss and compliments the individual, especially medium/short hair style pixies, men's cuts, bobs, layered shags, soft blended long layers, bold bangs, and razor cutting of all lengths.

name: Jennifer
desc: Jennifer loves to do highlights & corrective color, long layers, and fine hair. Please book in advance for appointments with Jennifer.

name: JESSI
desc: Jessi likes doing eye-catching color, fun & flirty cuts, and special occasion styles of all kinds. Jessi is also a braiding wizard.

name: JOSEPH
desc: Joseph loves clipper fades & classic men’s cuts, blended natural highlights, and cutting all hair - classic, funky and modern.

name: JOSIE
desc: Josie loves all things hair! She is great with all textures and lengths including men's barbering. She loves doing natural to dramatic color, helping you to look & feel your best!

name: LAURA
desc: Laura loves to shape long hair, loves doing any razor cut she can, and is an expert at curls curls curls. *Laura works every other Tuesday in Lakeview

name: LAUREN
desc: Laura loves to shape long hair, loves doing any razor cut she can, and is an expert at curls curls curls. *Laura works every other Tuesday in Lakeview

name: LIBBY
desc: Libby excels at short and/or creative haircuts. She loves to do bobs and is enjoys to work with all hair textures.

name: LISA
desc: Lisa loves to help clients feel confident and beautiful! She enjoys cutting long layers with movement, bobs with texture and short styles.

name: LO
desc: No two clients are alike and Lo feels the same should be true about their haircuts. From soft, diffused long layers, to perfectly shaped curls - she will find the best fit style for you! She specializes in wavy to curly textures.

name: OWEN
desc: Owen views hair as an artistic media outlet and ensures that every finished look is a masterpiece. Owen excels at creating short haircuts, crafting beachy blow dries, and enhancing hair’s natural texture.

name: PAIGE
desc: Paige loves doing all women's haircuts! From long to short, straight to curly - she's a master! She especially loves grey blending, wavy hair, crops, pixies & barbering.

name: REBECCA
desc: Rebecca loves to do beautiful, full arches, bridal & special event makeup, and to help her clients achieve the best results in skin care possible.

name: SARAH
desc: Sarah creates beautiful, effortless haircuts for all textures and specializes in waves and curls. She loves shorter women's cuts, men's cuts, and natural looking highlights/color.

name: SONIA
desc: Sonia loves to do soft, long layers, sun-kissed highlights, and classic haircuts with a modern twist.

name: STACIA
desc: Stacia loves long layers, adorable bobs, natural-looking highlights, and easy breezy hair

name: VALERIE
desc: Valerie (formerly Ava) loves to cut long layers & textured bobs, and styling voluminous blowouts.
